1. Required party: tank (plate, holy spells - Paladin), healer (cloth, holy - Priest), 3 DPS with two armor types: one plate, one cloth, one non-plate/cloth.
2. Metamorphosis restricts one DPS to Warlock (cloth), Frost/Fire forces Mage or Death Knight for Frost; choose Death Knight (plate) as DPS; bear is a Hunter pet (mail).
3. Kilt of the Forgotten One is leather, but no leather wearer in group.
4. All class/spec abilities must exist in their Wrath of the Lich King state (no Druid, Warrior can't cast Frost). Alphabetically: Death Knight, Hunter, Paladin, Priest, Warlock.
